replies.msg:
Dennis Lindsey on trading for Korver: &quot;I've been greatly offended by Joe Ingles' claim to be the greatest shooter on the planet. As a proud American, that he's comparing himself to Steph Curry, Klay Thompson, and Kyle Korver, I was offended.&quot;<br />
Lindsey: &quot;I wanted to make sure that he realizes not only is he not the best shooter in the world, with his leveraged-arm Aussie slingshot &mdash; like he's trying to shoot balloons in the Australian circus &mdash; he's no longer even the best shooter on the Jazz. That was my No. 1 goal.&quot;<br />
Joe Ingles' response: &quot;I might be out of here... (That he said that) is not a surprise at all. It feels like every time he sees me, he makes a joke to me about something. Now we have the two best shooters. It's all good.&quot;

